do with the fact that it's an inside show,  And they don't want people 
driving in/ out of the building, while the event is still on.   That place is 
a madhouse during set up/ take down times. 

  But I agree that  before 4pm I'm ready to head home.  I don't see why you 
couldn't drive into the grounds, without driving into the building, to get yr 
