NWVWClub.

I know that the Cascade Combis  (Vintage Meet) wanted to keep down the amount 
of people driving in/ out.  As there would be problems with people driving 
where there are loads of people walking.  

Don't California shows tend to open the gates at 7 am?  NW shows tend to 
start later than California shows.


